summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5392 for the improvement of 34th Avenue Southwest, from West Graham Street to a point approximately 310 feet south of West Morgan Street; and certain parts of certain oter streets and avenues; by constructing sewers and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 66524, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
